name: The Unspoken
description:
She's a force with no name. The destruction she brought was only the consequences
of her genius. Despised by her peers, she was better in every single way.
She could have made the world a better place. She could have use her
talents for the greater good. But not a single soul allowed her to do so.
She's barely mentioned anymore, only loosely, in this quite insulting quote:
"It's not over until the fat lady sings"
